WEBVTT

00:09.776 --> 00:11.644
You're traveling
through another dimension-

00:11.679 --> 00:15.398
a dimension not only of sight
and sound, but of mind,

00:15.433 --> 00:17.283
a journey into a wondrous land

00:17.318 --> 00:19.152
whose boundaries
are that of imagination.

00:19.187 --> 00:22.288
Your next stop,
the twilight zone.

